title: WooCommerce Multiple Customer Addresses 11.6 - WordPress Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org The WooCommerce Multiple Customer Addresses WordPress Plugin (WCMCA) will allow your registered customers to associate multiple addresses to their profile and optionally different products address on Checkout page! Nulled WooCommerce Multiple Customer Addresses WordPress Plugin now allows your customers to ship each item to different addresses! You have just to enable the special Shipping per product on the plugin options menu and that’s it! WooCommerce Multiple Customer Addresses WordPress Plugin Features add, edit and delete addresses disable multiple addresses for specific address type shipping email & email notification product shipping addresses product shipping addresses: handling fee add same items multiple times to cart admin user profile page extension admin order page eu vat identification number field on checkout
